      "name": "Electromagnetic Waves",
      "description": "Johnson raises his shield, continuously dealing 80( +60% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) to enemies in a fan-shaped area in the target direction and slowing them by 20%. Each instance of damage also increases the enemy's subsequent damage taken from the skill by 15% (up to 45%). This damage is increased by 60% against creeps. Johnson can cast Basic Attacks and skills for the duration.",
