    "ultimate": {
      "name": "Full Throttle",
      "description": "Johnson transforms into a car and begins accelerating over time. An allied hero can use (Hop In) when near Johnson to board the car (only 1 allied hero can ride with Johnson). The car will explode upon hitting an enemy hero or obstacle, dealing 300( +160% Total Magic Power)-450( +280% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) to nearby enemies, stunning them for 0.5-1s (scales with the car's speed before impact), and creating an electrified zone at the location. The zone continuously deals 60( +20% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) and slows enemies within. While in car state, tap (Brake) to stop immediately or hold (Nitrous) to continuously gain speed for up to 5s. Johnson's location will be revealed to the enemy team for 3s when casting this skill. (Passive): Johnson's Physical Defense is increased by 10%.",
